{"tid":2387721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府「諮詢」太空卡實名制　交立會文件訂明維持現狀「不是選項」","createTime":"2021-01-30T14:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T06:49:42.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"256920f66c34e05ff577de8b358bac3e6a13c100","tid":2387721,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">政府「諮詢」太空卡實名制　交立會文件訂明維持現狀「不是選項」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n港府昨日（29 日）突然宣布，就電話儲值卡（俗稱「太空卡」）實名登記制度展開「公眾諮詢」，諮詢期僅一個月、至 2 月 28 日。政府今（30 日）向立法會提交文件，列出立法建議，但在文件「其他方案」一項中寫明：「維持現狀並不是一個選項」，指匿名儲值卡削弱公眾對香港電訊制度穩健性的信心，是執法機關打擊涉及使用儲值卡罪案的「主要障礙」，必須為儲值卡及服務計劃下的各種服務，設立實名登記制度。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n.........<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E8%AB%AE%E8%A9%A2-%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%8D%A1%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E5%88%B6-%E4%BA%A4%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%A8%82%E6%98%8E%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E7%8F%BE%E7%8B%80-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85/?fbclid=IwAR3OOoIKk_KKeiwl53pYmS6gN1svD0cwVN1PqmokUfp0fA1emWRjtFrbHog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E8%25A8%2582%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%258B%2580-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2581%25B8%25E9%25A0%2585%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3OOoIKk_KKeiwl53pYmS6gN1svD0cwVN1PqmokUfp0fA1emWRjtFrbHog&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=711d59eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E8%25A9%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BB%25B6%25